You're not smiling. Not that face! Everybody smile!
别用那种表情，大家继续笑…

189
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:33,160
Just tell her what happened. It's not your fault.
乔伊，你怎么不实话实说？ 那又不能怪你

190
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:37,020
If we keep talking this way, won't we freak her out soon?
如果我们继续这样说话 会不会吓到她？

191
00:10:40,170 --> 00:10:42,570
Soon. I'm gonna be on soon.
很快…马上就轮我上场了

192
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:44,240
There I am!
那就是我！

193
00:10:46,740 --> 00:10:48,640
Sam Waterston!
山姆瓦特斯顿！

194
00:10:48,880 --> 00:10:50,970
No,no. That's me. That's me!
不对…那是我…

195
00:10:51,250 --> 00:10:53,370
No. Sam Waterston.
不是，那是山姆瓦特斯顿

196
00:10:53,580 --> 00:10:56,410
Crime Misdemeanor, Capricorn One.
“爱与罪” “摩羯一号大行动”

197
00:10:56,650 --> 00:10:59,710
She doesn't know "hello," but she knows Capricorn One.
她听不懂“你好” 却知道“摩羯一号大行动”

198
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:04,520
I need those earrings. We're leaving when the show's over.
菲比，我要那副耳环了 节目一演完我们就要出去

199
00:11:05,590 --> 00:11:07,860
But I already gave them back to you.
可是我已经还你了啊

200
00:11:10,030 --> 00:11:11,020
No,you didn't.
才没有

201
00:11:11,230 --> 00:11:14,900
I already didn't gave them back to you. That's what I said.
好，我已经还没还给你 我就是这样说的啊

202
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,930
Where's that other earring?
另一个耳环在哪里？

203
00:11:18,210 --> 00:11:20,330
It's not here,Phoebe. It's not here.
菲比，不在这里…

204
00:11:20,610 --> 00:11:22,510
I went to Chandler's last night.
我昨晚有去钱德和乔伊那里

205
00:11:22,710 --> 00:11:25,200
Make sure you check Chandler's jewelry box.
好，记得要检查钱德的珠宝盒

206
00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:29,410
Chandler has a jewelry box?
慢着，钱德有珠宝盒？

207
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:33,220
We have 10 minutes. Do you want me to get into that now?
好了，时间紧迫 你要我现在就跟你解释？

208
00:11:38,290 --> 00:11:39,730
Hey,Phoebe.
菲比

209
00:11:40,190 --> 00:11:41,590
How's that...
那个...

210
00:11:41,900 --> 00:11:45,200
...vegetarian pizza working out for you?
素食比萨… 你吃得还习惯吗？

211
00:11:47,230 --> 00:11:49,760
You and those vegetables have a real...
你和那些蔬菜 

212
00:11:49,970 --> 00:11:52,030
...thing going on,huh?
还真是有两下子，是吧？

213
00:11:54,810 --> 00:11:56,610
Why are you being weird?
你干嘛怪里怪气的？

214
00:11:58,050 --> 00:11:59,540
Do you like it?
你喜不喜欢？

215
00:12:01,780 --> 00:12:03,770
No. That'd be, "Why are you being cute?"
不喜欢，否则我就会问 “你干嘛装可爱”了

216
00:12:05,150 --> 00:12:07,210
Okay. I'm working on my flirting.
好吧，我在练习打情骂俏

217
00:12:07,420 --> 00:12:09,620
I did not get that.
原来如此，我没看出来

218
00:12:11,790 --> 00:12:14,060
So, Monica, do you like Law and Order?
摩妮卡，你喜欢看 “法网游龙”吗？

219
00:12:14,260 --> 00:12:15,420
Yeah,it's good.
喜欢，很好看

220
00:12:15,630 --> 00:12:18,720
I found out all this stuff about you. You like Law and Order...
我今天发现到了新的你 好比你爱看“法网游龙”

221
00:12:18,970 --> 00:12:22,270
...and you've flirted with every guy in the tri-state area.
还有你到处跟人打情骂俏

223
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:26,630
Okay,let me get this straight.
好，我来问个清楚 

224
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:29,780
It's okay for you to flirt, but not for me?
你可以打情骂俏，我却不行

225
00:12:29,980 --> 00:12:31,640
I'm glad we cleared that up.
真高兴我们把话说清楚了

226
00:12:32,580 --> 00:12:36,240
I'm sorry, but some things are different for men and women.
抱歉，但你听我说 男女有些事是不一样的

227
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:38,250
Teach me about men and women.
继续，开释我一些男女的差别

228
00:12:38,490 --> 00:12:41,650
I've already taught you so much already, but whatever.
好，虽然我已经教过你很多了

229
00:12:42,620 --> 00:12:45,420
When you flirt with a guy, you think,"No big deal."
你跟男人打情骂俏的时候 你觉得只是打情骂俏 没啥大不了的

230
00:12:45,660 --> 00:12:49,190
But he thinks,"Finally! Somebody who wants to sleep with me."
但对方会觉得 他终于找到人上床了

232
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:51,360
-No way! -It's true.
不可能 这是真的

233
00:12:52,130 --> 00:12:54,600
-Well,that's pathetic. -Again,true.
真可悲 这也是真的

234
00:12:55,640 --> 00:12:58,760
-This goes for all guys? -All guys that are awake.
男人都这样吗？ 醒着的男人都适用

236
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:00,630
We go to sleep.
等我们上床睡觉后

237
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:04,830
All guys from the other end of the world wake up and act the same way.
世界另一边的男人起床 继续做一模一样的事

238
00:13:06,150 --> 00:13:09,010
It's another commercial and I still haven't told her.
好，又进广告了 我还是没跟她说

239
00:13:09,220 --> 00:13:12,120
Joey,this is the last commercial.
乔伊，这是最后一段广告 

240
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:14,250
-You got 10 minutes left. -I know!
你只剩十分钟了 我知道…

241
00:13:14,460 --> 00:13:16,120
What am I gonna do?
你要我怎么办？

242
00:13:16,560 --> 00:13:18,860
You will not run out and leave her here.
不许你落跑，留她在这里

243
00:13:21,660 --> 00:13:23,390
Yeah,all right.
对，好啦

244
00:13:27,973 --> 00:13:29,167
乔伊？

245
00:13:29,800 --> 00:13:33,570
Joey's gonna be right back. Right back?
乔伊马上回来 马上回来？

247
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:36,840
Meanwhile,let's talk about you.
我们顺便来聊聊你吧

248
00:13:39,350 --> 00:13:41,340
So you're old and small.
你年纪大，个子小

249
00:13:48,790 --> 00:13:50,450
-Did you find it? -The earring,no.
找到没？ 耳环是没有

250
00:13:50,590 --> 00:13:52,120
But I found my sunglasses.
但我在沙发底下 找到我的太阳眼镜

251
00:13:52,330 --> 00:13:54,990
I've been looking for these since last summer.
我从去年夏天找到现在

252
00:13:55,500 --> 00:13:58,160
Those are mine. You borrowed them from me.
那是我借你的太阳眼镜

253
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:02,170
Okay. Calm down. Here they are.
好，别激动，还你就是了

254
00:14:02,842 --> 00:14:03,866
菲比

255
00:14:06,510 --> 00:14:09,670
-What do we do? -I don't know. I don't know!
我们要怎么办？ 我不知道…

256
00:14:09,910 --> 00:14:12,670
We'll just have to tell Monica,that's all.
我们只好老实跟摩妮卡说了

257
00:14:12,910 --> 00:14:15,880
Oh,God! She's gonna kill me.
老天，她一定会杀了我

258
00:14:16,820 --> 00:14:18,840
I could tell her it was all my fault.
我可以跟她说是我弄掉的

259
00:14:19,050 --> 00:14:20,580
Oh,that'd be great.
那就太好了

260
00:14:23,420 --> 00:14:25,050
Mon, could I talk to you?
摩妮卡，我有话要跟你说

261
00:14:25,330 --> 00:14:26,920
Yeah. What is it?
好，什么事？

262
00:14:28,260 --> 00:14:30,230
I lost one of your earrings.
我弄丢了你一支耳环 

263
00:14:30,430 --> 00:14:33,420
I'm sorry. I am so,so sorry.
对不起，我真的很抱歉

264
00:14:36,770 --> 00:14:40,400
All right,what can you do? If you lost it, you lost it.
好吧，都弄丢了还能怎样

265
00:14:40,670 --> 00:14:43,610
I'll replace it. I promise. I feel so terrible.
我保证会赔你一副新的 我真的很愧疚

266
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:46,570
That's fine. You didn't do it on purpose.
没关系，你又不是故意的

267
00:14:46,950 --> 00:14:48,850
Look at you. Come here.
瞧你难过的，来

268
00:14:51,590 --> 00:14:54,680
-You feel better? -Yeah. You're the best.
好点了没？ 有啊，你最棒了

269
00:14:55,390 --> 00:14:56,950
Okay, wait a minute.
好，等一等

270
00:14:58,230 --> 00:15:00,020
I can't do this.
我不能这样

271
00:15:00,260 --> 00:15:02,590
Listen, honey, it's not Phoebe's fault.
其实不是菲比弄丢的

272
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:04,520
She lent me the earrings.
她把你的耳环借我 

273
00:15:04,770 --> 00:15:08,260
I lost it. I'm so sorry,honey. I feel terrible too.
是我弄丢的，我真的很抱歉 我也觉得好愧疚

275
00:15:09,940 --> 00:15:13,070
That is exactly why I do not lend you stuff!
所以我才不借你东西！

276
00:15:14,580 --> 00:15:17,480
First,my jewelry. If it's not that,it's my sweater.
先是我的首饰 不是首饰，就是我的蓝色毛衣

278
00:15:17,710 --> 00:15:19,980
And if it's not that, it's my sunglasses.
不是蓝色毛衣 就是我的太阳眼镜

279
00:15:20,250 --> 00:15:22,110
-Your sunglasses? -Yes！
你的太阳眼镜？ 对！

280
00:15:22,380 --> 00:15:24,080
Oh,right.
对耶

281
00:15:25,220 --> 00:15:27,650
-Pizza. -Mine,mine,mine!
比萨外送 我的！…

282
00:15:29,320 --> 00:15:30,550
Okay,here goes.
好，要开始了

283
00:15:30,820 --> 00:15:33,990
Prepare yourselves for some class-A flirting.
准备见识一流的打情骂俏

284
00:15:34,230 --> 00:15:35,750
Okay,hold on.
等等…

285
00:15:36,669 --> 00:15:38,102
Okay.
我准备好了

286
00:15:39,230 --> 00:15:44,400
You have nothing to prove.And if you really like this girl, I don't think flirting is the right way
你犯不着这样 若你真的喜欢这个女孩 我也不觉得打情骂俏是…

288
00:15:46,110 --> 00:15:47,840
You'll see. Okay.
等着看就知道，好吧

289
00:15:50,740 --> 00:15:52,440
What's her name?
她叫什么名字？

290
00:15:53,150 --> 00:15:54,980
Caitlin!
凯特琳…

292
00:16:03,490 --> 00:16:06,080
We can't keep eating like this.
这样吃下去也不是办法

293
00:16:08,760 --> 00:16:10,990
It's $12.50.
12.5美元

294
00:16:11,136 --> 00:16:11,966
Okay.
好

296
00:16:16,700 --> 00:16:21,370
Do you make the pizzas in one of those wood-burning ovens?
你们做比萨 是用烧木头的炉子吗？

297
00:16:22,980 --> 00:16:25,840
No,actually,I think they're gas.
不是，其实是瓦斯炉

298
00:16:26,110 --> 00:16:27,270
Gas?
瓦斯炉？

299
00:16:30,450 --> 00:16:31,480
Intense.
真带劲

300
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:36,650
If this is how all the Gellers flirt, we don't have a problem.
如果盖勒家的人 都这样打情骂俏的话 我们就没有问题了

302
00:16:39,660 --> 00:16:42,220
You know that smell gas has?
你知道瓦斯的味道吗？

303
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:50,030
-Yeah. -They put that in.
知道 那是加进去的

305
00:16:51,140 --> 00:16:54,200
-What? -The gas is odorless.
什么？ 瓦斯其实是无色无味

306
00:16:54,480 --> 00:16:58,970
But they add the smell so you know when there's a leak.
加上味道是为了让人 在瓦斯漏气时能闻得出来

307
00:17:01,020 --> 00:17:02,210
Well,okay.
好吧

308
00:17:04,490 --> 00:17:07,250
A lot of other gas smells.
很多气体都有味道…

309
00:17:12,860 --> 00:17:14,230
Oh,the humanity!
救命喔

310
00:17:17,700 --> 00:17:20,430
Methane smells....
甲烷有味道…

311
00:17:21,670 --> 00:17:25,000
You know what? Actually, I really should go.
不好意思，我真的得走了

312
00:17:25,210 --> 00:17:28,170
-But I haven't paid you yet. -That's okay.
我还没付钱呢 没关系

313
00:17:28,380 --> 00:17:31,340
You guys have ordered so many that this one's on me.
你们点了那么多 这一个算我请的

314
00:17:39,090 --> 00:17:42,780
Was I talking to her about gas?
我是不是跟她说到瓦斯的事？

315
00:17:44,430 --> 00:17:46,720
More so than anything else.
那根本就是主题

316
00:17:48,460 --> 00:17:50,900
I found it interesting.
我觉得很有意思

317
00:17:53,670 --> 00:17:54,660
I'm sorry. No.
我很遗憾 不用…

318
00:17:54,800 --> 00:17:56,960
Don't worry about it.
别担心

319
00:17:57,240 --> 00:18:01,300
In nine years,she and l will be right there!
九年之后 我和她就能在一起了

320
00:18:07,780 --> 00:18:10,580
I'm gonna clear out some of these boxes.
好，我去清掉这些比萨盒

321
00:18:18,830 --> 00:18:21,060
-Ross? -Yeah? -What else do they add smell to?
罗斯？ 怎么了？ 还有哪些气体会加味道？

323
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:27,620
Caitlin! Caitlin!

324
00:18:27,900 --> 00:18:29,660
Hi,I'm Rachel.
我是瑞秋

325
00:18:30,400 --> 00:18:32,270
From upstairs? The ones with all the pizza?
住楼上的 叫一堆比萨的那家

326
00:18:32,470 --> 00:18:33,960
Was there a problem?
比萨有问题吗？ 

327
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:36,180
No,they're fine. Great pizza.
不是…比萨很好吃

328
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:39,440
But,actually,my friend Ross...
其实是我朋友罗斯的事

329
00:18:39,580 --> 00:18:43,410
...he gets nervous when he's flirting.
他只要打情骂俏就会紧张

330
00:18:43,920 --> 00:18:45,110
Oh,my God!
天啊

331
00:18:45,320 --> 00:18:47,410
-That was flirting? -Yeah.
他是在打情骂俏？ 没错

332
00:18:48,290 --> 00:18:49,980
I know,I know.
我知道你的感觉…

333
00:18:50,190 --> 00:18:53,460
I'm telling you, once you get past that part...
不过一旦过了那个阶段

334
00:18:53,660 --> 00:18:56,090
...where it feels like you wanna die...
那个让你想要自杀的阶段

335
00:18:56,330 --> 00:18:58,300
...he's a really good person.
你就会发现他是个大好人

336
00:18:58,500 --> 00:19:00,760
The guy with the gas?
开口闭口都是瓦斯的那个人？

337
00:19:01,300 --> 00:19:04,530
I'm telling you,he's really sweet and really funny...
他真的很体贴风趣

338
00:19:04,770 --> 00:19:06,830
...and he's just got a good heart.
还有一副好心肠

339
00:19:06,970 --> 00:19:11,740
You know,actually,I did think that he was cute and then he started talking.
其实我觉得他蛮可爱的 可是一开始说话就…

340
00:19:12,780 --> 00:19:15,150
See,there you go.
这就对了…

341
00:19:15,320 --> 00:19:19,380
-Besides, I think he really likes you. -Really?
而且我觉得他很喜欢你 真的吗？

342
00:19:19,590 --> 00:19:23,550
Well,we have seven people and 10 pizzas. What do you think?
我们七个人，却叫了十个比萨 这还不够明显吗？

343
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:26,590
I thought Joey was there.
我想说乔伊很会吃

344
00:19:28,160 --> 00:19:32,190
Yeah, no, but just I'm telling you he's worth a shot.
罗斯值得你去试试看

345
00:19:32,330 --> 00:19:35,670
Well, if he's so great why don't you go out with him?
如果他那么棒 你怎么不去跟他约会？

346
00:19:38,640 --> 00:19:41,040
Well,you know,at some point...
你知道吗？ 有朝一日...

347
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:45,200
...you and I may need to have a longer conversation.
...我们可能需要好好聊一聊

348
00:19:50,780 --> 00:19:51,770
Hey, Ross?
罗斯？

349
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:55,350
I just ran into Caitlin in the hallway.
我刚才在走廊遇到凯特琳

350
00:19:55,590 --> 00:19:59,360
You must be getting better at this flirting stuff than I thought.
你打情骂俏的技巧 肯定比我想像中更高明

351
00:19:59,560 --> 00:20:01,650
-What? -I don't get it,but she wanted me...
什么意思？ 虽然我搞不懂 

352
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:04,130
...to give you her number.
但她要我转交她的电话给你

353
00:20:09,070 --> 00:20:10,870
And she just gave you this?
她自己给你的？ 

354
00:20:14,210 --> 00:20:17,770
Rach, thanks. But I don't need you doing me any favors.
瑞秋，谢了 但我不需要你帮忙

355
00:20:17,980 --> 00:20:20,450
I didn't. She thought you were cute.
我没帮忙啊，是她觉得你可爱

356
00:20:21,920 --> 00:20:24,110
Well,that I can believe.
这点我倒是相信

357
00:20:25,890 --> 00:20:28,380
Hey,is the show still on?
还在演吗？

358
00:20:28,590 --> 00:20:29,780
Almost over,man.
快要演完了

359
00:20:30,060 --> 00:20:31,460
Hey,Nonnie.

360
00:20:32,060 --> 00:20:33,750
Is that the pope?
那是教宗吗？

361
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:38,090
Why am I looking?
我干嘛跟过去看？

362
00:20:38,830 --> 00:20:40,990
Oh, here I am! This is my big scene.
来了，我的主戏上场

363
00:20:41,670 --> 00:20:43,500
All right, back off!
快退后

364
00:20:45,470 --> 00:20:47,270
I got a gun!
我有枪喔

365
00:20:47,740 --> 00:20:49,170
I'm not afraid to use it.
用起来可不会手软

366
00:20:50,680 --> 00:20:52,080
-Joey! That's right, Nonnie.
乔伊！

367
00:20:52,350 --> 00:20:54,780
You couldn't have at least changed your shirt?
你起码也该换一件上衣的

368
00:20:56,650 --> 00:21:00,610
Now, I want a suitcase filled with $ 100,000
我要你在手提箱里 装满十万美元…

369
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:05,520
Filled with $ 100,000 in small bills.
装满十万美元的小钞

370
00:21:05,790 --> 00:21:07,920
And if I don't get Shoo!
若是我没拿到…

371
00:21:08,630 --> 00:21:10,430
And if I don't get it...
